use words\">House words</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Little_birds\" title=\"Little birds\">Little birds</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Master-at-arms\" title=\"Master-at-arms\">Master-at-arms</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_coin\" title=\"Master of coin\">Master of coin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_whisperers\" title=\"Master of whisperers\">Master of whisperers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mockingbird\" title=\"Mockingbird\">Mockingbird</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Name_day\" title=\"Name day\">Name day</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Oak\" title=\"Oak\">Oak</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Currency\" title=\"Currency\">Silver stag</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Small_council\" title=\"Small council\">Small council</a></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Storm_Dancer\" title=\"Storm Dancer\">Storm Dancer</a></i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Swan_ship\" title=\"Swan ship\">Swan ship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_on_Prince_Joffrey%27s_name_day\" title=\"Tourney on Prince Joffrey&#39;s name day\">Tourney on Prince Joffrey's name day</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_language\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Valyrian language\">Vulgar Valyrian</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel\" title=\"Valyrian steel\">Valyrian steel</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Littlefinger%27s_blade\" title=\"Littlefinger&#39;s blade\">Dagger</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_18&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>This page uses content from <b><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://con